TITLE: Registering Markdown Runtime Loader in PHP for non-Symfony projects
DESCRIPTION: This PHP code demonstrates how to register the Markdown extension runtime for non-Symfony projects, which is required for using the markdown_to_html filter.
SOURCE: https://github.com/twigphp/Twig/blob/3.x/doc/filters/markdown_to_html.rst#2025-04-14_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use Twig\Extra\Markdown\DefaultMarkdown;
use Twig\Extra\Markdown\MarkdownRuntime;
use Twig\RuntimeLoader\RuntimeLoaderInterface;

$twig->addRuntimeLoader(new class implements RuntimeLoaderInterface {
    public function load($class) {
        if (MarkdownRuntime::class === $class) {
            return new MarkdownRuntime(new DefaultMarkdown());
        }
    }
});
```

